---
title: Mexican Pork Tostadas with Cheddar Cheese & Greek Yoghurt
description: To make this speedy meal come together in 20 minutes, we started with the classic Mexican dish of tostadas! With a crisp, baked tortilla topped with a spicy and veggie packed pork chilli, plus creamy yoghurt and fresh herbs, this quick and satisfying dinner packs a ton of flavour in hardly any time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c7f5230e3f33912932c8942-08e65c21.jpg
